Northern Survey Supply will be showcasing its mining solutions at this year’s PDAC 2018 Convention in Toronto, Canada. The company will be exhibiting MOSS-specific products in an immersive environment such as total stations, multi-stations, tablet computers and software applications. PDAC International Convention, Trade Show and Investors Exchange is the world’s leading convention for people, companies and organisations in, or connected with, mineral exploration. In addition to meeting more than 1,000 exhibitors, 3,800 investors and 24,000 attendees from 130 countries, you can also attend technical sessions, short courses and networking events. The four-day annual convention held in Toronto, Canada, has grown in size, stature and influence since it began in 1932 and today is the event of choice for the world’s mineral industry.